title: Archer Avenue - I Was an Astronaut
description:
This record was recorded when Richard Edwards was 17, and Margot & the Nuclear So & So's was not yet in existence. Recorded in a basement, hear the elegant weavings of distorted guitars, steel guitars, and piano into a reverie of sadness. This rare album took me forever to find. It is by far one of my favourite Richard Edwards' album.
